{"tid":1080912,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"沙拿攬女球迷　被伊斯蘭教母親責罵","createTime":"2019-03-28T02:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T14:36:14.000Z","uid":54373,"like":213,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"163c07ecbd82cb38e270f0dd355e948ec841302d","tid":1080912,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:30:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2604462/org/ac96d7c649925b61e1a17ad35b29e77d.jpeg/qOnfRWIXCYwoTaGpJtzJI2sxemYJuhGcjge_nI4Hv5w?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2604462%2Forg%2Fac96d7c649925b61e1a17ad35b29e77d.jpeg%2FqOnfRWIXCYwoTaGpJtzJI2sxemYJuhGcjge_nI4Hv5w%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=6997d4ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2604461/org/8011a337987050f13740da3d4a344e28.jpeg/DugyWGpVH1L2_eXsM6Z8dobpwE9XtHcP3Pn-3Nz5_tw?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2604461%2Forg%2F8011a337987050f13740da3d4a344e28.jpeg%2FDugyWGpVH1L2_eXsM6Z8dobpwE9XtHcP3Pn-3Nz5_tw%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=59476996&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n利物浦射手穆罕默德沙拿，最近陷入入球荒，國際賽檔期趁機到杜拜鬆一鬆，亦出席了贊助商活動。<br />\n<br />\n沙拿日前在Instagram上載相片，在活動期間與女球迷擁抱的照片，換來母親用WhatsApp隔空訓示。<br />\n<br />\n雖然沙拿選擇用輕鬆手法回應母親，但仍有不少網迷批評該名埃及國腳行為不檢點。<br />\n<br />\n沙拿在今個國際賽檔期未有入選埃及大軍名單，獲得了休息的機會，趁機到杜拜休息，期間出席贊助商活動，引來黎巴嫩演員阿卜多（Jessy Abdo）、埃及時裝名人加莉比（Hadia Ghaleb）到場一睹沙拿風采，期間更有一名女性與沙拿擁抱。<br />\n<br />\n面對球迷的熱情，沙拿未有抗拒，卻惹來母親抗議及球迷的口誅筆伐。<br />\n<br />\n沙拿在IG上傳Story，上載了一張來自「Mama」的WhatsApp截圖，除了沙拿擁抱女球迷的照片外，還有短訊，大意為「如果我見到你父親這樣做，我會立即要求離婚！」沙拿在截圖上加了幾個哈哈大笑的Emoji。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2604559/org/d35f5cd454f8d1880226bd980fb6fbb0.jpg/GvfyXikMQ1HUQVtZS1FQ-tbkM8C2F8tKUk4xKVJOMSk?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2604559%2Forg%2Fd35f5cd454f8d1880226bd980fb6fbb0.jpg%2FGvfyXikMQ1HUQVtZS1FQ-tbkM8C2F8tKUk4xKVJOMSk%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=351f26f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿卜多無辜受牽連<br />\n<br />\n沙拿被母親訓斥，亦有不少保守網民在網上口誅筆伐，批評沙拿行為不檢點，作為有婦之夫應該拒絕球迷等等。更有球迷將該名女球迷誤認為阿卜多，在網上肆意批評，令到該名黎巴嫩女演員要公開澄清自己並非該名女性。<br />\n<br />\n沙拿於2013年與同學Magi結婚，翌年於倫敦，當沙拿效力車路士時，妻子誕下女兒Makka。據了解，Magi是一名生物技術人員。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2604463/org/62377a81fd200e30a79351ac20d3dc95.jpg/fTI9nx86_B5ZNWDlsF5LvDpC3hl3FmcGSE4_MUhOPzE?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2604463%2Forg%2F62377a81fd200e30a79351ac20d3dc95.jpg%2FfTI9nx86_B5ZNWDlsF5LvDpC3hl3FmcGSE4_MUhOPzE%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=7b4c9939&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙拿與妻子Magi結婚6年，育有一女Makka。（網上圖片）"},{"pid":"5f95e1859b7bce32b973f92aaef4016728487f88","tid":1080912,"uid":54373,"like":80,"dislike":1,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:31:14.000Z","msg":"「Mama」的WhatsApp截圖，除了沙拿擁抱女球迷的照片外，還有短訊，大意為「如果我見到你父親這樣做，我會立即要求離婚！」"},{"pid":"52db96a786a9a0787e2b0fd2e4fc601bd8dee40b","tid":1080912,"uid":5649,"like":287,"dislike":5,"score":282,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:32:20.000Z","msg":"條女咁正 隻回教豬點忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e05787018aaeff226c5041c8179e049a3816690","tid":1080912,"uid":115150,"like":344,"dislike":5,"score":339,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:33:58.000Z","msg":"個老婆咁c9 沙拿想偷食都正常 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"504e5a5ab13f0ef35166d448c879f698146e8c75","tid":1080912,"uid":128568,"like":264,"dislike":2,"score":262,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:34:22.000Z","msg":"佢老婆又真係頹左D既"},{"pid":"0d77bffff5db9de4cd0e9395912a3e93c882fb2b","tid":1080912,"uid":59806,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:34:40.000Z","msg":"有無第二張相條女ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8bffb08d74a2ac1a3a874de80f0f74f2bd955e","tid":1080912,"uid":45189,"like":111,"dislike":2,"score":109,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:39:45.000